content:
The third day of Not in Our School's Week focused on "Ability Awareness" and featured events including food served by <a href="http://www.adascafe.org/">Ada's Cafe</a>, a performance by the American Sign Language class and a table sponsored by the Best Buddies club. Students and teachers wore the color purple in support of the theme of Ability Awareness.

Photos by Becca Raffel and Callie Walker.

